**Form Configurations** give you full control over both the look and feel of a form and its behavior.

## Configuration Properties

| Property                 | Description | Options | Default | Required |
| ------------------------ | ----------- | ------- | ------- | -------- |
| `name`                   |             |         |         | Yes      |
| `resource`               |             |         |         | Yes      |
| `api_call_notifications` |             |         |         | No       |
| `async_callback_actions` |             |         |         | No       |
| `authorization_policies` |             |         |         | No       |
| `callback_actions`       |             |         |         | No       |
| `configuration`          |             |         |         | No       |
| `default_payload`        |             |         |         | No       |
| `email_notifications`    |             |         |         | No       |
| `flash_alert`            |             |         |         | No       |
| `flash_notice`           |             |         |         | No       |
| `redirect_to`            |             |         |         | No       |
| `resource_owner`         |             |         | `self`  | No       |
| `sms_notifications`      |             |         |         | No       |
| `spam_protection`        |             |         |         | No       |

